FREDERICK H. THOMPSON COMPANY, Appellant, v. The MAGNAVOX COMPANY, Appellee. No. 6448. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 11, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and NETERER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation of counsel for tho respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed without costs to either party; mandate forthwith.
